<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.graphics.ITextureSampler.SetTextureFilterMode" Title="SetTextureFilterMode method" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.ITextureSampler">ITextureSampler</PageRef> ->
    SetTextureFilterMode
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>SetTextureFilterMode</TypeRef> method specifies the filter mode to use when sampling from the texture.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[void SetTextureFilterMode(FilterMode filterModeShrink, FilterMode filterModeExpand);]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Argument list">
      <ArgumentList>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="FilterMode" Name="filterModeShrink">
          The filter mode used when the sampled texture is minified.
        </ArgumentListEntry>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="FilterMode" Name="filterModeExpand">
          The filter mode used when the sampled texture is magnified.
        </ArgumentListEntry>
      </ArgumentList>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="See also">
    <PageRefList>
      <PageRefListEntry PageName="cobalt.graphics.ITextureSampler">ITextureSampler</PageRefListEntry>
    </PageRefList>
  </Section>
</XMLDocContent>
